My sil ky love
My sil ky love
My sil ky love
My sil ky love
Every hour of the day
whenever I think of you
these impatient feelings
simply overflow.
Even though it is easy to say I love you
when you stand in front of me
my personality stands up and gets in my way.
I can usually pull through with my assertiveness
that is just how I am.
But no matter how hard I try, I cannot break the wall that is between us.
I want you to realise my feelings.
So I always send a gaze
of I really love you your way
with all of my courage!
My flimsy silky heart.
After meeting you, I finally realised
that I am really clumsy when it comes to love.
The scars from love that I would almost forgotten
have started to ache all of a sudden.
Someday, like how I normally would...
I must say I love you, or else I will become even weaker.
On the nights I cannot sleep
I sigh alone.
H ow is everyone?
I feel a little lonely.
Within the vast world, a single seed
extended its roots
and put out a fruit that was still unripe.
The fruit that I wish would turn orange soon
The fruit that I wish would turn orange soon
is bathed in your light.
The ideals and dreams just swell -
H ey, feel it.
Today, I tried eating an orange
Today, I tried eating an orange
but it was so sour I cried.
I could not leave it behind like I have been
so I ate it all.
I love it I feel like crying.
I love it I love it.

Beneath the Fir Tree
Are your feelings of guilt gone?
Go!
Do not you think Kushieda-senpai is acting weird?
You are right.
I mean, she is a weird person by nature,
but she is been spacing out a lot more than usual recently.
What the heck am I doing?
Oh yeah, the big year-end sale is coming up soon,
and then spring cleaning is after that.
From the deepest parts of the cupboards to the tatami mats,
I will clean every inch.
No!
No!
You are thinking about it wrong; it is Christmas.
Christmas!
Huh?
Oh, I am so looking forward to it.
I guess I have to be good for the time being,
because he is probably near the skies of Japan right now.
Who?
Do you really need to ask?
Santa!
Santa Claus!
Give me that, I will help you carry it.
Are you okay?
It will be great if he visits our house again this year.
What is wrong?
You know,
I love Christmas!
I know you love Christmas, but why so much?
Do you need a reason to love Christmas?
The street decorations are sparkling beautifully...
Hey, you will spoil your dinner!
I know, that is why I am only eating one.
No, you do not understand.
We are going to celebrate the end of your suspension tonight.
Also, yellowtails are a natural product, so they are really expensive.
You should at least pretend to appreciate them because of the price.
Yay, yay!
Yellowtail hotpot!
One more time.
There are a lot of yellowtails, yay.
One more time!
So...
Did you get closer to Minorin during my suspension?
No progress at all, right?
Sheesh, what did you do with the chance I gave you?
B-But it could not be helped...
If you are not here,
Kushieda will not come to the meeting place in the morning,
and she will eat lunch with some other girls.
Then after school, she is busy with club -
With all that waiting, do you think you are the faithful dog, Hachiko?
Do you really think Minorin will come for you if you wait long enough?
Fool.
Stupid.
Dumb dog.
Idiot Ryuuji.
Although I was planning to say that...
You have already said it all out loud.
Well, I guess not progressing at all is something that cannot be helped.
Fine, I will come up with a plan for you.
Huh?
It is Christmas, so I will be reborn as an angel of love to help you.
T-That is so wrong.
Say whatever you want, I am a living saint right now.
Saint?
I thought you were an angel.
My bad, I meant angel.
In order to give everyone a happy and joyful Christmas,
I am prepared to take off one or two pieces of clothing, or even take it all off.
So just leave it to me!
So, do I look like an angel?
No,
and the crumbs are falling onto your head.
No way!
Get them off!
Taiga-san is here!
Taiga-san is back at school!
Taiga-san, we appreciate your effort!
What is with you guys?
We became your fans after we saw that fight.
The battle between the boss and the Palmtop Tiger...
It was actually your victory, right?!
You fought the first and final battle against her for your love...
Quiet down!
That fight was very difficult and caused a lot of hardship.
However, the last person standing was the victor.
In other words,
I was the true victor!
Come on, do not mess around.
Let us go, Taiga.
My tense thigh, and...
W-What is going on?
Minorin, I am back at school!
Stop singing weird songs and give me a hug!
Let go of me!
I am a human!
Minorin, I missed you a lot!
Why did not you wait for us at the meeting place?
To be honest, I overslept so I had to rush here today.
That is why my thighs are so sore.
Wait, how did I get here before you guys?
W-Well...
We were surrounded by some weird guys.
Anyway, Kushieda -
Shut up, brat!
Why did I say that?
Or did I make a bad joke?
Crap!
I screwed up!
Sorry!
Forget it!
Mornin', Takasu.
Oh, Taiga, long time no see.
Hey, are you doing all right?
Huh?
Kushieda broke down again?
I screwed up so badly.
I should seriously become a monk.
Just let me be bald for now.
No...
Why is a high school girl like you wearing a bald wig?
Aisaka!
W-What is going on now?
Good morning, Aisaka.
K-Kitamura-kun, good morning...
Takasu, good morning to you too.
W-Why?
It is morning, that is why I am saying good morning.
No!
I mean your pose!
Oh, I am...
Full of...
I am full of admiration!
My feelings for Aisaka cannot be shown by just kneeling,
which is why I am lying down.
Aisaka!
Yes?
Regardless of who it is for, you should not fight anymore.
If you cannot forgive someone, you have to talk to me about it first.
So yeah, I saw it with my own eyes.
Yes.
I mean, he is an assistant professor,
but I saw him coming out of a casino!
Oh, that confirms it.
He was not late for the date because of his work,
but because he was playing slot machines!
Yeah, so I messaged one of my girlfriends...
Because I was being treated badly by him, I asked her what I should do.
Oh...
Then I found out something else.
Such a breathtaking development...
It seems there is no such occupation as an assistant professor.
There is only assistant teacher.
That means...
Ever since then, I have not heard a thing from him.
What did you do to make our teacher cry, Kitamura?
Let us just pretend we do not know it is actually Yuri-chan.
Cheering For Your Love was brought to you by Kitamura Yuusaku,
Yeah...
the God of Broken Hearts.
Our guest today goes by the pseudonym of Y-chan.
God of Broken Hearts?
What is that?
Oh, because of that confession,
Kitamura has become the school's love saint -
I mean, he became a religious figure for those wanting to confess to someone.
Huh?
They say Kitamura will take all the bad luck away.
It is something like The Lucky God of Broken Hearts Legend.
Let me remind you, final exams are coming up.
That is so stupid.
Why do the people of our school love to believe legends so much?
Everyone, are you prepared?
I, the God of Broken Hearts, should also start studying,
Do not you think this broadcast is really annoying?
but not everything goes my way.
Why did he bring up the topic of studying?
Should not the title be Cheering For Your Love?
Taiga is listening to it, so shut up,
or else she will not be able to hear the touching stories of Master Kitamura.
Taiga, are you all right?
Can hear it clearly?
Huh?
Yeah, I am fine.
Speaking of which, Taiga is being really modest today.
I mean, she would have killed Haruta had he done that any other day.
You noticed?
Yeah, I am being good.
Good?
Well, I am being good because it is nearly Christmas.
I mean, look, Santa is watching us.
Oh, what was that?
Are you stupid?
I cannot believe you think Santa really exists.
That is not like you at all.
Stupid Chi', it is nearly Christmas!
If you are naughty, Santa will not visit your house.
There is definitely something strange about you.
Did something happen during your suspension?
Or is this a sign of death?
Are you going to die tomorrow?
Why am I going to die tomorrow?!
Both of you, cut it out!
Thank you for listening!
Next...
After the dreaded exams, it will be Christmas,
the time that everyone is looking forward to!
Now an announcement from the student council.
After the ceremony on Christmas Eve,
there will be a Christmas party in the gym.
You have to come as couples.
Troubled by love?
Cannot ask him or her out?
Why do not you try to invite the person you have feelings for to the party on that romantic night?
Christmas...
Listen, Ryuuji.
This is the perfect chance.
You have to invite Minorin to the Christmas Eve party.
Huh?
Do not Huh? me!
You have to confess to her in a snap!
C-Confess?
Y-You are asking for the impossible.
You have to do it.
It is Christmas Eve.
It is the holy Christmas Eve.
I am the angel of love!
I am the holy child of Christmas and the model for being good!
Even Santa is looking at me!
Huh?
In order to make your love life successful,
I will become Cupid!
No, thanks.
Well, well...
H-Hey!
So...
Do I look like Cupid?
No, you do not.
You really do not.
My god, are not you slow?
The special party for cool guys is in here...
Merry Christmas!
Oh, god!
Look, Nanako!
That guy over there is really cute!
I am totally fine with that type of guy!
Oh my, what a gentleman.
There is a lot of time left, so if you are hungry, eat this first!
Huh?
Where are you going?
What did you say?
Am I really that boring?
It is Christmas, and I am waiting for you to do fun things to me...
Exactly, let us do fun things together!
Let us get naked!
We are naked!
What?
Someone cuter?
So you want a cuter and prettier Santa?
Are you talking about me?!
That was the dream I had.
What a pervert.
You are the worst.
Gosh, Haruta-kun...
Wait, why am I the most unfortunate?
Putting that aside,
let us talk about the real party.
First, we have to decide who will be staff.
Taiga, go for it.
Did not you say that you love Christmas?
Yeah, good idea.
I-If everyone is asking me to go for it, I guess I will have to.
Come join me, you sugary-slug-dog!
S-Sure.
Wait, what type of dog did you say I am?
Minorin, come join us!
Sorry.
I will pass this time.
Why?
I am really not in the mood to go to a Christmas party.
I mean, it is not the time for me to have fun.
What is wrong, Kushieda?
I screwed up unbelievably during the softball match,
and we lost because of that.
It is really embarrassing.
If I go and have fun at a party during a time like this,
I do not think the club members will look up to me anymore.
Also, I have to practise for a match I have after New Year's.
Minorin...
Y-You do not need to help out, just come for the party and -
I will not be going to the party.
Then, I will help you guys set stuff up.
Ami-chan, you are going to?
Then, I will help too!
I am really looking forward to the party!
We will heat it up using the power of Class 2-C!
Oh, my...
What is with that look?
You do not want to be with me?
Let me make this clear, Takasu-kun.
It is in your best interest to be nice to me.
Why?
This sort of plan is my specialty.
I will determine whether the party will be a success or not,
and it is also up to me to get that unhappy somebody to come.
Huh?
What is wrong?
Oh, so you want to join us?
If that is the case, we would be glad to have you.
I said I am not going to.
Minorin!
Wait, Minorin!
Huh?
Ryuu-chan, you are going out?
Taiga-chan is going too?
Yeah, to study for our finals.
We are meeting Kitamura and the others at the restaurant we always go to.
There is a salmon fillet in the frying pan, remember to heat it up before you eat it.
Eh?
Ya-chan will be giza lonely gansu!
W-What is with that giza and gansu?
Ryuu-chan, do not you know?
It is a popular saying right now.
Some new person at work told me about it.
Young people say things like gansu,
and giza sounds cute, right?
Ya-chan is giza-ly smart!
Cut it out.
It sounds really wrong.
How does it sound wrong?
This is giza-ly good!
It is tera-ly correct!
Inko-chan, take care of Yasuko for me.
You are the only one I can rely on.
Too bad!
No!
No!
No!
No!
Such a rebellious reaction!
What is going on, Inko-chan?
What happened to your cute and honest side?
Oh, I know.
It must be the book you borrowed.
I am sorry, Inko-chan!
I did something really stupid!
I will never cook you!
I promise!
R-Really?
Of course!
S-Seriously?
I am serious!
What are you guys doing?
Hey, did you bring it?
Of course.
It is safe in here.
The prize I got at the cultural festival for winning the Mr. Lucky Guy contest...
They call it The Boss's Notes.
There will be nothing to be afraid of if we use this to study.
But to be honest, this belongs to Kushieda.
She let me win with her.
She said she cannot come because of her job, so it cannot be helped.
Quit living in the past like an old person.
I am not living in the -
Then, stop standing there.
We are going to study at the place where Minorin works,
so you should try and have a chat with her before everyone arrives.
Y-Yeah!
Kushieda took the day off.
When you are ready to order, press the button.
Hey, Ryuuji.
Do you think Minorin is avoiding you?
W-Why would she?!
You guys do not speak to each other at school,
and I was the one who invited her to the study session.
That is because you told me to leave everything to you.
Do you guys even talk to each other at all?
N-No...
Going to work was an excuse,
and she said she is not going to the party.
She is feeling down because she screwed up during a match.
Is not it your specialty to make everything better in times like these?!
But...
It is really weird.
I do not even know how to support her now.
Your relationship with Minorin seems different from before.
Before, you guys were more...
Yo, Takasu and Taiga,
sorry to make you wait.
I am really hungry.
O-Oh...
Yo.
It is really cold today.
Wearing a winter coat on cold days makes you really warm!
Maruo, you should buy one for yourself.
Kihara?
What are you doing here?
This is not like you at all.
I also want a copy of The Boss's Notes!
And I cannot study by myself...
Come on, let us sit down.
All right, this table is ours.
Hey Taiga, stand up.
Haruta, go over there.
Okay.
Kihara, you are sitting next to Takasu.
Wait...
Here you go.
I will sit next to Haruta, and Kitamura, you are sitting at the other table.
W-Wait!
I want to sit there too!
No, um, well...
Girls should sit together!
Right, Taiga?
Let us do that.
Do not be so selfish.
Do you not want to sit next to Takasu?
No, it is not that!
Let us order now.
Everyone is going to the drink bar, right?
All right.
No point in everyone getting up for drinks,
so I will get them for all of you.
I-I want something hot!
Okay.
Taiga, go to the drink bar with him.
Is not it cold today?
Hey, what are you plotting?
What are you talking about?
Do not play dumb!
Why are you pairing Taiga and Kitamura up on purpose?
Oh, we have been found out.
Whatever, I want you to help out too.
Huh?
I think Kitamura and Taiga would make a good couple.
Oh, I think so too.
Look, Kitamura is probably still upset about the Boss rejecting him, right?
Do not you think a new love would help cure him?
T-That might work.
Taiga likes Kitamura.
I am serious.
I do not think you have noticed it.
You are surprised, right?
I was surprised too.
After all, you are the closest one to her since you take care of her and stuff.
Yeah, so being surprised is only natural.
You guys are wrong.
Huh?
What?
Never mind.
You guys are right.
Wow!
Taiga, it seems you really like this.
Yeah, it is really beautiful!
Taiga likes Kitamura.
Have not I known that for a long time?
But why am I...
Hey, Takasu-kun.
I do not understand.
Hey!
Takasu-kun, what do you think?
Do you think it would be good for Taiga and Maruo to go out with each other?
No, that is...
Actually, it would be too sudden.
Exactly!
You agree, right?
Even though everyone says it, it is not like that, right?
Wait a second.
What do you mean by everyone?
If Taiga goes out with Maruo,
you do not think it will be interesting, right?
Huh?
Everyone says you are gentle, and you love to care for others,
Wai -
but you actually like Taiga, right?
I will support you, I swear!
Do not tell me you like Kitamu -
Hey, Kihara!
Hurry up.
Coming!
Takasu-kun, do not give up!
Come on!
Stop annoying me!
I said I am coming!
This is some super confusing Guns N' Roses.
It will definitely be interesting!
It will get your spirits up!
That is why you have to come to the party, Kushieda.
I cannot be my usual self anymore.
Yes, surely...
Probably...
